content.rendered:
The Shade Outdoor Lounge Set is a new addition for this summer, available in a choice of colours and with optional cushions.

The Shade Outdoor Lounge Set is made with a durable UV resistant reinforced resin which will not unravel or rust, ensuring minimal care is required.

Requires basic self assembly. Held in stock for delivery in 2-3 working days.

Dimensions:

SOFA: Height: 800mm, Width: 1510mm, Depth: 660mm & Seat Height 420mm.

ARMCHAIR: Height: 800mm, Width: 760mm, Depth 660mm & Seat Height 420mm.

COFFEE TABLE: Height: 330mm, Width: 900mm & Depth: 500mm.
